on't%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20Budget%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20year%20did%20not%20make%20any%20changes%20in%20tax%20slabs%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20only%20announced%20relief%20for%20old%20and%20disputed%20tax%20demands%20up%20to%20an%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20line%20with%20expectations%2C%20as%20any%20major%20tax%20relief%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20populist%20move%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20due%20in%20two%20months.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20of%20violation%20of%20the%20model%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20a%20third%20term%20in%20the%20Centre%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20interim%20Budget%20in%202019%20-%20the%20year%20PM%20Modi%20won%20a%20second%20term%20-%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20had%20kept%20the%20tax%20slab%20unchanged%2C%20but%20increased%20standard%20deduction%20for%20salaried%20people%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20all%20tax-related%20matters%20have%20been%20left%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20interim%20Budget%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20had%20also%20hiked%20the%20tax%20deducted%20at%20source%20(TDS)%20limit%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20for%20post%20office%20savings%20and%20bank%20deposits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20year%20the%20BJP%20defeated%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20the%20then%20Finance%20Minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20in%20his%20interim%20Budget%20had%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20tax%20laws%2C%20but%20tweaked%20indirect%20taxes%20for%20a%20small%20set%20of%20sectors.%20He%20reduced%20excise%20duty%20from%2012%20per%20cent%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20some%20goods%2C%20and%20gave%20relief%20to%20the%20automobile%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20was%20no%20expectation%20of%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20slabs%20in%20this%20interim%20Budget%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20about%20a%20possible%20increase%20in%20the%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regime%20does%20not%20allow%20taxpayers%20to%20claim%20deductions%2C%20but%20eases%20the%20tax%20slabs%20for%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20incomes%2C%20while%20the%20old%20regime%20has%20a%20maximum%20tax%20slab%20of%2030%20per%20cent%20from%20a%20lower%20threshold%2C%20but%20also%20allows%20claims%20to%20be%20filed%20for%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20hike%20in%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20taxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706776020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F6kah06f8_income-tax-_625x300_06_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-tax-slab-trends-in-interim-budgets-why-they-dont-change-4972703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20interim%20Budget%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20year%20did%20not%20make%20any%20changes%20in%20tax%20slabs%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20only%20announced%20relief%20for%20old%20and%20disputed%20tax%20demands%20up%20to%20an%20extent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-tax-slab-trends-in-interim-budgets-why-they-dont-change-4972703%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-tax-slab-trends-in-interim-budgets-why-they-dont-change-4972703%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Funion-budget-2024-tax-slab-trends-in-interim-budgets-why-they-dont-change-4972703%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20Foreigners%20And%20A%20Sophisticated%20Drug%20Lab%20At%20%26quot%3BLuxury%26quot%3B%20Home%20Near%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20foreign%20nationals%20and%20a%20luxurious%20house%20near%20Delhi%20-%20a%20detail%20that%20didn't%20mean%20much%20to%20anyone%20until%20it%20was%20known%20that%20the%20team%20of%20four%20was%20using%20the%20property%20to%20produce%20%26quot%3Bfine-quality%26quot%3B%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lab%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bluxurious%20and%20lonely%20private%20place%26quot%3B%20at%20Alestonia%20Estate%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Greater%20Noida%20was%20busted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20police%20recovered%20445%20grams%20of%20fine-quality%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drug%20and%2020.5%20kg%20of%20raw%20materials%20that%20included%20one%20kg%20of%20pseudoephedrine%20-%20an%20ingredient%20for%20the%20illicit%20manufacture%20of%20methamphetamines.%20Sophisticated%20equipment%2C%20including%20a%20heating%20mantle%20machine%20and%20high-quality%20face%20masks%2C%20were%20also%20recovered%20from%20the%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigerian%20national%20Eze%20Uchenna%20James%20(49)%2C%20Alitumo%20Ifedi%20Shedrack%20(28)%2C%20Eze%20Ibe%20Emeka%20Chibuzo%20alias%20Iko%20(56)%20and%20Kenyan%20national%20Ivo%20Osita%20alias%20Usta%20alias%20Osey%20(44)%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Eze%2C%20Alitumo%20and%20Ivo%20were%20previously%20arrested%20and%20convicted%20in%20drug%20trafficking%20cases%20and%20were%20out%20on%20conditional%20bail%2C%20according%20to%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Dwarka)%20Ankit%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20bust%20was%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20operation%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20the%20suppliers%20of%20narcotics%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2027%2C%202023%2C%20a%20team%20of%20the%20Anti-Narcotics%20Cell%20of%20Dwarka%20district%20got%20a%20secret%20tip-off%20about%20a%20Nigerian%20national%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20drug%20syndicate.%20The%20team%20conducted%20a%20raid%20and%20caught%20Eze%20from%20Uttam%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Eze's%20arrest%2C%20his%20associate%20Alitumo%20was%20caught%20from%20the%20same%20area%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%20on%20January%2011%20and%20about%20100%20grams%20of%20methamphetamine%20drug%20was%20recovered%20from%20his%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20Alitumo%20along%20with%20Ibe%20and%20Ivo%20used%20to%20manufacture%20fine-quality%20methamphetamine%20drug%20in%20the%20Greater%20Noida-based%20lab%2C%20a%20raid%20was%20conducted%20and%20all%20of%20them%20were%20caught%20on%20January%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20accused%20used%20to%20distribute%20the%20drugs%20to%20their%20potential%20customers%20in%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706774580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ftuagh2dg_methamphetamine-drug-bust_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnoida-news%2Fmethamphetamine-drug-lab-greater-noida-4-foreigners-and-a-sophisticated-lab-at-luxury-home-near-delhi-4972135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20foreign%20nationals%20and%20a%20luxurious%20house%20near%20Delhi%20-%20a%20detail%20that%20didn't%20mean%20much%20to%20anyone%20until%20it%20was%20known%20that%20the%20team%20of%20four%20was%20using%20the%20property%20to%20produce%20fine-quality%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drugs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnoida-news%2Fmethamphetamine-drug-lab-greater-noida-4-foreigners-and-a-sophisticated-lab-at-luxury-home-near-delhi-4972135%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnoida-news%2Fmethamphetamine-drug-lab-greater-noida-4-foreigners-and-a-